# Cursor Configuration for Stock Market Predictor

## Project Description

This is a stock market trend predictor in order for users to see which investments will help make them money in trading.

- Includes helpful technical analysis
- Stunning UI
- Beginner friendly

## Project Architecture

- Python backend
- Deployed to Heroku on CNB

## Dependency Management
- Use `mise` to manage and run dependencies for this project
- Run commands through mise: `mise run <task>` or `mise exec -- <command>`
- Python version is managed via mise (3.12)

## Development Workflow
- Use `mise run dev` to start the Flask development server
- Use `mise run install` to install dependencies
- Always use mise when running Python commands or installing packages

## Testing
- Typecheck when done making a series of code changes
- Prefer running single tests, not the whole test suite, for performance

